Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userid": 1,
  "type": "checking",
  "balance": 500
}

###

### Create a new saving account for a user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userid": 12,
  "type": "saving",
  "balance": 1000
}

###

### Get all accounts for a user
